# =============================================================================
# LoyaCareCRM - PRODUCTION Environment Configuration Template
# =============================================================================
# ⚠️  IMPORTANT: This file is for REFERENCE ONLY!
# 
# Environment files (.env) are automatically created/updated by GitHub Actions
# using secrets from GitHub Environment: production
# 
